Privacy Policy for Evergreen
Introduction
Welcome to Evergreen ("we," "our," "us"). Your privacy is critically important to us. This Privacy Policy describes how we collect, 
use, and safeguard your information when you visit our app. By using our app, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this policy.

Information We Collect

Personal Information

  Username: Required for account creation and login.
  Password: Required for account creation and login.

How We Use Your Information
  Personal Information
  Account Management: Your username and password are used to manage your account and provide secure access to your account.
  Security: To ensure the security of your account, including verifying your identity when you log in.

Sharing Your Information
We do not share your personal information (username and password) with any third parties. Your information is stored securely and is only used as described in this Privacy Policy.

Data Security
We use industry-standard security measures to protect your personal information. However, no method of 
transmission over the internet, or method of electronic storage, is 100% secure. 
While we strive to use commercially acceptable means to protect your personal information, 
we cannot guarantee its absolute security.

Your Rights
You have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal information. If you wish to exercise these rights, please contact us at [contact email].

Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page. You are advised to review this Privacy
